{"tid":2338784,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"人間最溫暖的天使！聖誕節前夕IU捐款一億做慈善，幫助低收入學生入學！","createTime":"2020-12-24T08:35:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T13:15:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"42c63e631c0484a7eaa27075aac3825c0d5ebb3d","tid":2338784,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_5cf900e8fca72c97f05c8660d832c3dd/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-12-24/132546-890293.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_5cf900e8fca72c97f05c8660d832c3dd%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-12-24%2F132546-890293.jpg&h=3b6e7f55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nIU出道到現在一直都致力於做善事，真的是位非常善良的天使～<br />\n<br />\n專門救助低收入家庭與孩童的慈善機構「綠色雨傘兒童基金會」，表示在24號平安夜這天，收到IU為了紀念聖誕節，而捐贈了一億韓元（約兩百七十萬台幣）的善款！<br />\n<br />\n綠色雨傘兒童基金會對於IU的善款非常感謝，這筆資金也將會用於低收入、單親、隔代教育的家庭，日常所需的生活費還有小朋友們的入學費用。<br />\n<br />\n從出道開始就默默行善的IU，每年都會向不同所需的單位捐款，光是可知的金額就高達二十億韓元以上（約五千四百萬台幣），今年為了疫情也投入不少善款。<br />\n<br />\n其實今年的兒童節時，IU就曾向綠色雨傘兒童基金會捐出一億韓元，更是在自己的生日時，跟粉絲一起做公益，再捐出一億三百萬韓元，都是希望能夠幫助到社會上需要幫助的地方～<br />\n<br />\n(圖片或影片來源：IG@dlwlrma)"},{"pid":"403798ac36b060d1dae77dee1efd77132eaabe5b","tid":2338784,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"人美心善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdf7df83fd35565eb3a845cd81d21df1eaf2edb4","tid":2338784,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"403798ac36b060d1dae77dee1efd77132eaabe5b","tid":2338784,"uid":229026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-24T08:36:17.000Z","msg":"人美心善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 